Entries.default: "Hey, it's an arena my god hasn't walked through."
"This reminds me of tales of Old Vailia. They all end badly."
"I have performed for bigger audiences, but I say this one will do."
"Center of attention, an adoring crowd... I could get used to this."
"I bet they've got all kinds of snacks!"
"Cap... Something ain't right bout the air in this place. Too full up of souls."
"An edifice to mindless violence. And crowded with more than the souls of the living."
"I want to disapprove of this place, but I don't want to get in the way of idiots killing each other."
"Hoping we fare better in this nonsense than my last crew."
"We will give them the best show, ta?"
"A party?! Let's get good and squiffy, captain!"
